Multivariable Calculus | Green's Theorem

\begin{array}{l}\n\text { Ere } 810^{\circ} \mathrm{S} \\\n\oint_{\partial D} P d x+Q d y=\iint_{D}\left(\frac{\partial Q}{\partial x}-\frac{\partial P}{\partial y}\right) d A\n\end{array}[imath]\text { Ere } 810^{\circ} \mathrm{S} [/imath] [imath]\oint_{\partial D} P d x+Q d y=\iint_{D}\left(\frac{\partial Q}{\partial x}-\frac{\partial P}{\partial y}\right) d A[/imath]
